        "url": "https://x.com/thenanyu/status/2040177368187212157"
      },
      {
        "text": "https://t.co/2xXYdLA1tY\n\nThey may roll their eyes.. and then one day they will finish a project. \n\nAnd that project will have 40 incomplete issues. And they will want to group them by usecase. And for some of them, they will want to create new projects and other ones they will want to cancel or rout",
